data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET!!! Introducing a stunning Custom Contemporary Home with impeccable designs surpassing new construction. Enjoy the dramatic entryway with beautiful, curved staircase, flowing seamlessly into Large Primary Suite, exercise room and Formal Dining area with exquisite Crown Molding details, and Butler's Pantry. Unwind in the Huge Family Room with Grand Fireplace, natural light, and Large Kitchen/Breakfast area, complete with appliances. Upstairs boasts three Large Bedrooms, including an exquisite guest suite and Large Gameroom for unlimited enjoyment. Two more bedrooms share a Jack and Jill Bathroom, complete with walk-in closets. Experience complete tranquility and privacy with no back neighbors, and abundant storage throughout. Conveniently located near 99/249 for easy access to everything. Ready to move-in, this luxurious must-see property is an opportunity you don't want to miss.
